Package: growkar
Title: Tidy Analysis of Microbial Growth Curve Time Series
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pooja", "Sethiya", 
           email = "poojasethiya24@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to import, validate, visualize, summarize, and model
    microbial growth curves from optical density time-series data. The package
    supports a tidy workflow centered on canonical sample, time, and OD
    columns, empirical estimation of growth rate and doubling time,
    exponential-phase detection, model-based fitting with logistic and
    Gompertz growth models, and coercion to Bioconductor-compatible
    SummarizedExperiment containers.
